    "Similarly, Hagendorff (2023) introduce machine psychology as an umbrella term, which we will adopt throughout the paper.",
    "Pellert et al. (2024) and Hagendorff (2023) argue that machine psychology differs from LLM benchmarking by focusing on diagnosis rather than establishing performance.",
